    "code_Data": "<section class=\"trf-section\">\n  <h2>Protection against the spread of fire — Form A.22</h2>\n  <p class=\"subtext\">IEC 61010-1 · Table/Form A.22 · Record protection method per Clause 9.1 (a, b, or c)</p>\n  <div class=\"table-wrap\">\n    <table class=\"trf-table\" aria-describedby=\"fire-table-desc\">\n      <caption id=\"fire-table-desc\">Record each source of hazard and the chosen protection method with details and verdict.</caption>\n      <thead>\n        <tr>\n          <th scope=\"col\" class=\"col-item\">Item</th>\n          <th scope=\"col\" class=\"col-source\">Source of hazard or area of the equipment (circuit, component, liquid, etc.)</th>\n          <th scope=\"col\" class=\"col-method\">Protection Method<br><span class=\"muted\">(9.1 a, b or c)</span></th>\n          <th scope=\"col\" class=\"col-details\">Protection details</th>\n          <th scope=\"col\" class=\"col-verdict\">Verdict</th>\n        </tr>\n      </thead>\n      <tbody>\n        <tr>\n          <td data-label=\"Item\">1</td>\n          <td data-label=\"Source of hazard or area\">Power supply PCB near mains input (non-limited circuit)</td>\n          <td data-label=\"Protection Method\">9.1(b)</td>\n          <td data-label=\"Protection details\">Basic insulation across opposite polarity; flammability V‑1 enclosure baffle; wiring VW‑1</td>\n          <td data-label=\"Verdict\">Pass</td>\n        </tr>\n      </tbody>\n    </table>\n  </div>\n</section>\n<style>\n  :root { --bg:#0b0f1a; --card:#121826; --text:#e6edf6; --muted:#9aa6b2; --accent:#5aa9e6; --border:#253046; --stripe:#171f2e; --ok:#39d98a; --fail:#ff6b6b; }\n  .trf-section{background:var(--bg);color:var(--text);padding:1rem;border-radius:12px;font-family:system-ui,-apple-system,Segoe UI,Roboto,\\\"Helvetica Neue\\\",Arial,\\\"Noto Sans\\\",\\\"Liberation Sans\\\",sans-serif}\n  .trf-section h2{margin:0 0 .25rem 0;font-size:1.25rem;letter-spacing:.2px}\n  .trf-section .subtext{margin:0 0 1rem 0;color:var(--muted);font-size:.9rem}\n  .table-wrap{background:var(--card);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:12px;overflow:hidden}\n  .trf-table{width:100%;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:0}\n  .trf-table caption{text-align:left;padding:.75rem 1rem;color:var(--muted);font-size:.9rem;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border)}\n  .trf-table thead th{position:sticky;top:0;background:linear-gradient(180deg,#1a2335 0%,#162032 100%);color:var(--text);text-align:left;padding:.75rem 1rem;font-weight:600;font-size:.9rem;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);z-index:1}\n  .trf-table tbody td{padding:.75rem 1rem;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);vertical-align:top;font-size:.92rem}\n  .trf-table tbody tr:nth-child(odd){background:var(--stripe)}\n  .trf-table .muted{color:var(--muted);font-weight:400;font-size:.8rem}\n  .col-item{width:64px}.col-source{width:35%}.col-method{width:120px}.col-details{width:40%}.col-verdict{width:120px}\n  @media (max-width:860px){.trf-table thead{display:none}.trf-table tbody tr{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr;padding:.5rem 0}.trf-table tbody td{display:grid;grid-template-columns:160px 1fr;gap:.5rem;border:0;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border)}.trf-table tbody td::before{content:attr(data-label);color:var(--muted);font-weight:600}}\n  td[data-label=\\\"Verdict\\\"]{font-weight:600}\n</style>"
